     It's hard to get close to the flames after the fingers have been burnt.  And then you get half-assed should we--shouldn't we entries into delicate situations like Somalia.  Meanwhile we turn a blind eye to Indoneasian aggression in East Timor, and did virtually nothing aboput Pol Pot; because the Vietnamese were involved in pushing him out.<br><br>
